              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33074350/" class="">不太“剑桥”的段落</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/metalbrick/" class=" " title="砖！砖！砖！">砖！砖！砖！</a>
                (电池电量低，无法回复请见谅。)
              
